-- Greece Seeks to Export Solar Power by 2015, Manager Magazin Says
-- B y   S t e f a n   N i c o l a
-- 2012-03-19T08:01:55Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-19/greece-seeks-to-export-solar-power-by-2015-manager-magazin-says.html
Greece  is seeking to export power
generated by solar panels before 2015, Manager Magazin reported,
citing Energy Minister  George Papaconstantinou .  In the coming weeks, the country will adopt legislation to
simplify permitting and aims to connect its first 300-megawatt
plant by the end of 2013 as part of the Helios solar-energy
project, the German magazine said, citing Papaconstantinou.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Stefan Nicola in Berlin at 
